                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-89-off524 t18281023-89-cd525"></join>, 2 shillings, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18281023-89-victim539" type="victimName">
                        Louis Adolphus 
